LEWANDOWSKI.

00:17:14.410 --> 00:17:16.278
un du host im gezen?

00:17:16.290 --> 00:17:19.552
ye. er i-, er iz dokh oykh geven...

00:17:21.469 --> 00:17:26.028
az di polyakn zaynen gevezn WORSER vi di daytshn.

00:17:25.474 --> 00:17:26.716
vi azoy?

00:17:26.376 --> 00:17:29.844
z-, zey flegn zayn, geyn in POLICE,

00:17:30.650 --> 00:17:38.427
arbetn in POLICE bay di daytshn. hobn di daytshn zey zey gezogt, tut mit di yu- yidn vos ir vilt.

00:17:41.616 --> 00:17:52.471
