ikh hob gehat, der farm. oyf a farm, YOU'RE WORKING HARD, ober di luft iz BEAUTIFUL, YOU UNDERSTAND?

00:18:12.301 --> 00:18:24.088
kenst gedenken vo-, vos di doytshn hobn gemakht, epes shteyt oys mer vi epes andersh, vos hobn di, dortn gemakht in Dokshits?

00:18:25.930 --> 00:18:31.500
zey flegn, EXCUSE ME, zey flegn, s'iz geven a yudnrat.

00:18:31.600 --> 00:18:38.562
zey hobn oysgeklibn eyn yid. un vos me hot gedarft fun, zey, flegn zey heysn brengen yunge m- meydlekh.

00:18:43.271 --> 00:18:50.083
un eltere mentshn flegt men traybn oyf arbet un nit gebn esn, un nit PAY.

00:18:51.431 --> 00:19:00.426
un vi me hot gemakht a geto fun fir STREET, fun fir hayzer, fun fir STREET hayzer, eyne.

00:19:00.640 --> 00:19:07.680
flegt zayn in an erekh azoy vi do, eyn ROOM flegt zayn fir FAMILIES.

00:19:07.813 --> 00:19:12.072
vi azoy hobn zey gekrign tsu esn?

00:19:11.835 --> 00:19:12.727
esn?

00:19:12.877 --> 00:19:18.375
dos vos du host, es.

00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:20.874
s'iz nit geven keyn STORE.

00:19:21.613 --> 00:19:27.202
un host nit getort koyfn mit, bay, mit bay eynem geCATCHt a pekl puter

00:19:27.289 --> 00:19:28.521
in POCKET...

00:19:30.395 --> 00:19:32.510
YOU UNDERSTAND?

00:19:32.590 --> 00:19:33.624
THAT'S ALL.

00:19:34.682 --> 00:19:41.106
ikh ken reydn teg un vokhn, un monatn un yorn, shoyn nor genug az ikh hob

00:19:42.333 --> 00:19:46.153
a bisele m-, mayn.

00:19:47.940 --> 00:19:49.851
ikh bin fun ayzn.

00:19:49.851 --> 00:19:53.324
ayzn UNK RUST oykh.

00:19:53.324 --> 00:19:54.924
YOU UNDERSTAND?

00:19:59.236 --> 00:20:02.985
 vil-, vilst az ikh zol zingen a geto-lidele?

00:20:02.990 --> 00:20:05.205
yo, du vilst?

00:20:05.149 --> 00:20:09.882
vi ale forn, YOU UNDERSTAND, JEWISH?

00:20:10.198 --> 00:20:15.179
in mitn dem veg dort ligt eyn tayere blum.

00:20:15.179 --> 00:20:22.382
zi ligt un zi foylt un shrayt un veynt, pamelekh, zet vi ir geyt.

00:20:22.382 --> 00:20:28.424
ir geyt un tsetret eyn tayere BLUME mit eyn fartike kveyt.

00:20:28.424 --> 00:20:32.660
trogt mikh ahin fun vanen ikh bin

00:20:32.660 --> 00:20:36.159
vu me hot mikh in ershtn geflantst.

00:20:36.159 --> 00:20:41.169
tsetrotn un tsenetst, tseveykt un tsekvetsht

00:20:41.169 --> 00:20:45.859
di bleter, arop fun kolir. YOU UNDERSTAND?

00:20:46.150 --> 00:20:50.152
ikh lig oyf dem mist, der regn, er gist.

00:20:50.260 --> 00:20:53.890
un keyner hot keyn rakhmones oyf mir nit.

00:20:53.890 --> 00:21:01.755
azoy vi, azoy vi ikh hob gefunen, ot der vayb, vinter, NAKED, iz zi gelegn oyf a PILLOW.

00:21:01.755 --> 00:21:06.294
oyfn FLOOR, oyf shney, mit...

00:21:06.276 --> 00:21:08.583
ikh vil tsurikgeyn a bisl.

00:21:08.714 --> 00:21:11.845
ven ven di doytshn iz arayngekumen in geto,

00:21:11.800 --> 00:21:12.390
ye?

00:21:13.015 --> 00:21:18.310
du host gezen vi zey hobn genumen dayn tate un dayn mame?

00:21:18.950 --> 00:21:20.470
du host gezen vi zey?

00:21:20.134 --> 00:21:20.730
NO.

00:21:20.470 --> 00:21:21.005
NO.

00:21:21.010 --> 00:21:23.376
vi azoy hostu gevust az di...

00:21:23.210 --> 00:21:30.997
ikh fleg zay-, ikh fleg brengen, s'iz geven tsen mayl fun may-, vu ikh hob gelebt.

00:21:31.173 --> 00:21:39.603
tsu di, fleg ikh brengen tsvey mol a vokh tsu farkoyfn EGGS, milkh, SOUR CREAM.

00:21:39.656 --> 00:21:43.122
puter. vi zogt men in english puter?

00:21:42.794 --> 00:21:43.510
BUTTER.

00:21:43.490 --> 00:21:44.325
BUTTER.

00:21:44.660 --> 00:21:47.434
ikh, ikh kum tsu geyn.

00:21:47.434 --> 00:21:49.955
s'i-, s'iz ofn di WINDOWS.

00:21:50.210 --> 00:21:52.420
s'iz keyner nito in shtub.

00:21:57.555 --> 00:22:02.745
ir, ir darft lebn tsu tsvey hundert yor, shver tsu tseyln.

00:22:04.536 --> 00:22:06.588
SO vi hostu oysgefunen...

00:22:04.997 --> 00:22:09.204
az az az ir hot dos nit gezen mit ayere oygn.

00:22:09.500 --> 00:22:14.133
vi hostu oysgefunen vu zey zenen genumen?

00:22:14.374 --> 00:22:16.012
di mame un di tate.

00:22:15.770 --> 00:22:24.990
az ikh bi-, ikh bin gekumen tsum shtub un ikh ze az s'iz keyner nito. hob ikh, hob ikh a freg geton, zogn zey

00:22:25.638 --> 00:22:28.943
farges. zey lign shoyn.

00:22:29.377 --> 00:22:36.498
un s'iz geven nit vayt. a fertl kilometer tsum grub f- fun di shtot.

00:22:37.072 --> 00:22:40.511
bin ikh avekgegangen.

00:22:44.078 --> 00:22:52.711
oft mol vos a mentsh ken iberlebn mit UNK farfirn. nor eyn zakh bin ikh HAPPY,

00:22:53.153 --> 00:22:58.802
vos ikh hob aroy-, untergeleygt a mine, zenen mir arayngegangen, d- dray mener

00:22:59.240 --> 00:23:04.270
yidishe un mir hobn untergeleygt a mine tsvishn Molodetshno un Vilne.

00:23:04.270 --> 00:23:08.047
a groyse, a groyse BRIDGE.

00:23:08.114 --> 00:23:13.441
mir hobn untergeleygt a mine un mir hobn gevust az se geyt a TRAIN.

00:23:13.441 --> 00:23:16.242
vayl me flegt hern vi der TRAIN geyt.

00:23:16.242 --> 00:23:26.042
hobn mir untergeleygt a a a groyse, azoy vi di di di amerikaner, dray BOYS hobn untergeleygt a a BOMB. ikh gib dir EXAMPLE.

00:23:26.042 --> 00:23:29.831
un s'hot oyfgerisn der brik, un der TRAIN in vaser.

00:23:29.968 --> 00:23:39.635
UNK ikh hob, ikh nekome opgenumen. vayl arayngevorfn dray, aropgevorfn dray dray teyner-, TRAINS, eyner mit

00:23:40.692 --> 00:23:43.932
mit JETS,

00:23:44.100 --> 00:23:47.855
eyner mit tankS, un eyner mit SOLDIERS.

00:23:47.953 --> 00:23:56.033
vu iz dos, vu, ikh vil tsurikgeyn a minut fun di fun di mayse. v- v- vu bistu geganen

00:23:56.463 --> 00:24:02.963
ven di doytshn zenen arayngekumen, vi azoy hostu zikh geratevet fun zey?

00:23:58.791 --> 00:23:59.574
ye?

00:24:03.110 --> 00:24:05.400
ikh veys aleyn nit vi azoy.

00:24:05.799 --> 00:24:10.467
mit vemen ikh hob ge-, bin ikh geven in a grupe fun tsvantsik man.

00:24:10.495 --> 00:24:12.236
alemen oysgeharget.

00:24:13.444 --> 00:24:15.348
ikh bin eyner geblibn lebn.

00:24:14.928 --> 00:24:16.101
vi azoy?

00:24:16.101 --> 00:24:18.353
ikh veys aleyn nit vi azoy.

00:24:18.273 --> 00:24:19.532
du host geloyfn?

00:24:19.712 --> 00:24:20.812
?

00:24:20.565 --> 00:24:22.307
du host geloyfn?

00:24:21.968 --> 00:24:23.630
ikh bin gelofn.

00:24:24.382 --> 00:24:32.392
bay tog fleg ikh zayn bahaltn unter a unter a UNK. bay nakht fleg ikh geyn

00:24:32.973 --> 00:24:35.782
arayngeyn betn a shtikl broyt.

00:24:35.364 --> 00:24:37.317
AND bist gekumen...

00:24:36.468 --> 00:24:43.676
gey-, geyn a kuk ton vu me git di, di PIGS esn,

00:24:44.458 --> 00:24:48.200
efsher iz dortn fun zey a bisl epes geblibn?

00:24:48.988 --> 00:24:51.692
vi lang iz azoy geven?

00:24:51.775 --> 00:24:53.770
oy.

00:24:55.061 --> 00:24:59.103
a zeks akht monat.

00:24:59.280 --> 00:25:04.571
AND du host geloyfn fun Dokshits biz vu?

00:25:05.569 --> 00:25:14.229
mit di, fu- fun Dokshits, me me m'hot undz avek-, me m'hot undz tsunoyfgeklibn, ts- tsvantsik, finf un tsvantsik yunge mener,

00:25:14.751 --> 00:25:19.670
un me hot undz avekgetribn oyf a farm ar- arbetn.

00:25:20.081 --> 00:25:33.394
flegt men darfn arbetn, un der vos SOMETIME er filt NO gut., WARUM arbetn SIE nit? liber her, ikh fil nit gut.

00:25:33.406 --> 00:25:34.890
avekgefirt.

